# Ignore DOI and academic publisher URLs that block automated link checkers
# These links are valid but return 403 for automated tools

# DOI resolvers (all DOI links)
https://doi.org/*
https://dx.doi.org/*

# AIP Scitation (Materials Project paper)
https://aip.scitation.org/doi/10.1063/1.4812323

# APS Physical Review Letters (CGCNN paper)
https://journals.aps.org/prl/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevLett.120.145301

# model-viewer asset in docs/2_cgcnn.md: ../assets/nacl.glb is correct for the
# built MkDocs site (page renders at /2_cgcnn/, asset at /assets/nacl.glb) but
# resolves outside docs/ in the source tree
file://.*/assets/nacl\.glb

# GitHub's /releases/latest always 302s to the latest tag by design
https://github.com/jcwang587/cgcnn2/releases/latest
